OOC: Far from that!

BIC: A capsule that had been deriving since a long time in space was 
entering earth's orbit. It was an old capsule, about from the Great 
War. It entered the atmosphere, fire surrounding it. It went down 
about in central africa. The robot inside was still alive, but the 
energy would be out in just a few cycle. The capsule's computer sent 
out a distress signal.
